  <h1>Morning Prayers</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">On rising, to begin the day.</p>

  <div class="dev-banner ui" data-pagefind-ignore>
    🚧 <strong>Placeholder / scaffold.</strong> The full text and ordering are still being
