      <li><strong>Third Hour:</strong> <Ref ref="PSA 16" />, <Ref ref="PSA 24" /></li>
      <li><strong>Sixth Hour:</strong> <Ref ref="PSA 53" />, <Ref ref="PSA 54" />, <Ref ref="PSA 90" /></li>
    </ul>
  </p>

  <PrayerScripture ref="PSA 50" label="Psalm 50(51)" />

  <p>
    Glory to the Father and to the Son and to the Holy Spirit, now and ever and unto ages of ages. Amen.
  </p>

  <NiceneCreed heading="The Symbol of Faith" />

  <h2>Prayer of St. Macarius the Great</h2>

  <p>
    O God, cleanse me, a sinner, even though I've done nothing good before Thee; yet deliver me from the evil one, and let Thy will be done in me, that I may open my unworthy lips and praise Thy holy Name, of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit, now and ever and unto ages of ages. Amen.
  </p>

